{{flavour|A magical device which throws small bolts of destructive energy.}}

When evoked, the '''wand of magic darts''' fires a [[Magic Dart]] at your target, dealing weak but unavoidable damage. Although not a very powerful [[wand]], melee-oriented characters may want to use it to weaken enemies at range before entering combat, at least in the early game. These wands often generate with a lot of charges, unlike the more powerful wands. It can have at most 48 charges.

Due to the wand of magic darts' low damage output, enemies with significant [[AC]] will often negate its damage output entirely. Don't expect to accomplish much firing this at an oncoming [[orc warrior]] or other heavily armoured foe; it's much better suited for use against halberd-wielding [[gnoll (monster)|gnolls]] and other high-damage, low-durability threats.

==History==
*Wands of magic darts were removed in [[0.18]].
*Prior to [[0.16]], this wand could hold up to 24 charges.
